the_vault:vitalis.name: Vitalis Plate
the_vault:vitalis.lore: Woven with devotion, its embrace strengthens the body, filling the heart with vitality beyond measure. Few armours guard life as fiercely as this.

the_vault:ender_rings.name: Ender Rings
the_vault:ender_rings.lore: A pair of rings that allow the bearer to bend space.
